            <!-- Stemmatics -->
            <note type="stemmatics">OY lists 33 mss., of which four can be considered historic, although none is definitive. The note on NO 2406 cannot be regarded as completely reliable, and the text in Shehit Ali 1375 is dated at 722H only on the basis of other works in the collection. But the work appears in other very good collections, such as Carullah 986 and Beyazit 3750, and has been very widely copied. It is also mentioned in the FM, and there is internal evidence of authenticity in the text.</note>
